<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.9">
<l>kaittalat tuḷḷamā ṭaḻiyak kaṇ ṇālaṅkaḷ ceytivaḷai</l>
<l>vaittuvait tukkoṇṭeṉ ṉavāṇiyan nammai vaṭuppaṭuttuñ</l>
<l>ceyttalai yeḻunāṟṟup pōlavaṉ ceyvaṉa ceytukoḷḷa</l>
<l>maittaṭa mukilvaṇṇaṉ pakkal vaḷaravi ṭumiṉkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is the use in keeping her [here],</l>
<l>conducting marriages so that the wealth [we have] on hand is spent?</l>
<l>[It will only] bring reproach to us.</l>
<l>Like a seedling reared for transplanting that grows in a field,</l>
<l>Leave [her] to grow up with the huge, dark cloud hued [lord],</l>
<l>[he can] do whatever he [wants with her].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
